{"tid":1633261,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理非] 升級！Thanksgiving Day","createTime":"2019-10-07T03:10:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T04:05:31.000Z","uid":50598,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3adfbaad9818c3a89c42aab6baa27111f39e5084","tid":1633261,"uid":50598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:10:52.000Z","msg":"係時候為運動注入創意原素<br />\n之前都有巴打提倡過黃店感謝祭 其實仲可以發大黎搞 全民感謝日<br />\n1. 幫襯黃店<br />\n2. 多謝「守護孩子」對我地既不離不棄 <br />\n3. 多謝勇武義士為香港依個家付出 可以去探監 可以去唱歌聲援<br />\n4. 多謝國際對我地既支持 連儂場表達+眾籌登報<br />\n5. 多謝父母對我地既諒解<br />\n6. 多謝咁多位家長一直以黎既義載<br />\n7. 多謝文宣組不眠不休既消毒<br />\n8. 仲有更多更多不能盡錄<br />\n<br />\n更多既實際行動留俾各位巴絲出招<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重點係夠warm 等運動既每個角色都知自己不孤單 又可以全民參與<br />\n更加可以俾到畫面國際 眾所尻知 Thanksgiving Day係美加既傳統節日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0418b182fb6e2721bd0e708552e45679f2b8938c","tid":1633261,"uid":50598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:14:29.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c364f6c27c1b10753674fd93032a20f23c9a92a","tid":1633261,"uid":50598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:19:42.000Z","msg":"2/100 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf8ec05bae51c833f058e7ccd450c6bd161355a1","tid":1633261,"uid":50598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:24:33.000Z","msg":"3/100<br />\n洗版bot去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d91ddbfbee4a892b25fa2873ef452fe11bf16eca","tid":1633261,"uid":50598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:31:08.000Z","msg":"4/100"},{"pid":"5289aa26290258c1711f262f46ae9a9598c9536a","tid":1633261,"uid":50598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:37:09.000Z","msg":"5/100"},{"pid":"98d371c1009cbdd36035b80462ca52c13b8a679e","tid":163326